data.description: Adventure awaits at this two-story oasis, perfect for outdoor enthusiasts and their gear. Nestled on an oversized lot, it boasts a fenced yard, RV carport with electrical hookup, and ample space for all your toys. Dive into the screened-in saltwater pool or gather around the fire pit under the stars. Inside, pleasantly updated, natural light pours through tall windows into the expansive living area, reaching up to sky-high ceilings, and blending effortlessly with a kitchen designed for social gatherings around a spacious eat-in bar. The master suite on the ground floor offers serene comfort, while upstairs, two additional bedrooms and a loft with a closet provide ample space for a growing family or guests. This home is a haven for those who love the great outdoors, offering the perfect blend of adventure and home comfort.
